a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-red-400 hover:text-red-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/zh?tab=mp3\">去提取<!-- --> →</a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-4 bg-gray-900/50\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-12\">使用流程</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-red-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-red-600/30\"><span class=\"text-white font-black text-lg\">01</span></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">粘贴链接</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">复制任意 YouTube 视频链接，粘贴到输入框中。</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-red-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-red-600/30\"><span class=\"text-white font-black text-lg\">02</span></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">AI 处理</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">系统提取字幕并通过 AI 生成摘要和关键要点。</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-red-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-red-600/30\"><span class=\"text-white font-black text-lg\">03</span></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">获取结果</h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">查看 AI 摘要、复制字幕或下载视频/音频。</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12\">为什么选择 YTTools？</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6\"><div class=\"mb-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 